telligenceoffer</a>尝试免费 30 天数字订阅</p>]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 25 Aug 2023 09:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> /内容/orqtfbmktq3qd55hnq55j7tf6msi9vpp</guid><link/> https://www.economist.com/podcasts/2023/08/25/an-expanded-brics-is-not-necessarily-a-stronger-one </item><item><title><![CDATA[The fall of Yevgeny Prigozhin]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="css-phnw8u ex4i8i00"><style data-emotion="css j1vyw6">.css-j1vyw6 img{display:block;}.css-j1vyw6 .e16qazw92{margin-top:0.25rem;}</style><figure class="css-j1vyw6 e12yhaj20"><img theme="[object Object]" alt="" loading="lazy" width="1280" height="720" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 1440px) 700px, (min-width: 1280px) 50vw, (min-width: 960px) 66vw, 95vw" srcset="https://www.economist.com/img/b/256/144/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 256w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/360/202/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 360w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/384/216/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 384w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/480/270/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 480w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/600/337/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 600w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/834/469/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 834w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/960/540/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 960w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/1096/616/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 1096w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/1280/720/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 1280w, https://www.economist.com/img/b/1424/801/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg 1424w" src="https://www.economist.com/img/b/1424/801/90/media-assets/image/20230825_FLP003.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></figure></div><style data-emotion="css tati6o">.css-tati6o{font-family:var(--ds-type-system-serif);font-size:var(--ds-type-scale-4);font-weight:normal;line-height:var(--ds-type-leading-upper);}.css-tati6o a{